### 4.5 SSE 流式推送设计

教案生成采用 Server-Sent Events 逐段推送，避免教师等待：

```
教师点击"生成教案"
  → business-api 接收请求，创建任务ID
  → business-api 异步调用 ai-service
  → ai-service 通义千问 API (stream=True)
  → 每收到一个 token，通过 SSE 推送给前端
  → 前端 ProseMirror 实时渲染
  → 生成完成后，business-api 存储完整教案

SSE 事件格式：
event: lesson_plan_chunk
data: {"field": "objectives", "content": "1. 知识与能力目标：...", "done": false}

event: curriculum_alignment
data: {"objective_id": "obj-1", "standard_code": "3.2.1", "match_score": 0.92}

event: lesson_plan_complete
data: {"lesson_plan_id": "lp-xxx", "edit_url": "/lesson-plans/lp-xxx"}
```

